OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fovernight with a mix of cloud and
OL,7,Fclear spells. Turning chilly in any
OL,8,Fprolonged clear spells, with some
OL,9,Fpatchy mist and fog developing. Breezy
OL,10,Faround the Moors.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FLow cloud locally lingering
OL,13,Falong southern coasts. Otherwise, a
OL,14,Fdry day with an increasing amount of
OL,15,Fpleasant spring sunshine. Feeling mild
OL,16,Fwith just a slight breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
